data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful Move in Ready 2 Story Home located in  a Cul-de-sac Street! Features: 5 Bedrooms, 3 Baths, upstairs laundry room, Open floor plan with a formal living room, dining room, spacious kitchen area and a center island, family room with fireplace and slider door leads to the backyard. Porcelain tile flooring throughout the first floor approximately 5 months old.1 bedroom and 1 bathroom downstairs. Upstairs master bedroom with walk-in-closet, bathroom with dual sinks, separate shower enclosure and a separate tub. Upstairs additional 3 bedrooms share a bathroom with dual sink and a tub/shower combo. Spacious backyard perfect for entertaining. Solar panels. Don't miss out this opportunity. Must See, Must See!
